{
  "stem": "3631.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we knew it was coming, and then we had to get-- those in the ghetto had to-- had to get permission again to move out, and-- and who couldn't make it, I don't remember what-- probably didn't get permit-- they were either shot or sent out.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At that time, there was, I think hundreds of children in the ghetto who were-- who were shot, and-- and older people, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, no furniture or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could take a suitcase or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then, we had no room where to put it, the things, because we had-- the barracks had 600 or 800 people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No-- no bunks, even.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had individual platforms-- planks, in three tiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at one point, we had-- I just read this-- we had 28 centimeter of sleeping space per person, which is about-- a little less than 12 inches.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That meant when-- when one turned around, the-- the other one had to turn around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was really bad until it got organized.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a lot of cruelty, a lot of-- a lot of beating and a lot of-- I remember in the-- the first few days while I was not allotted to any particular place, I was hanging around the office, they were-- they would take Jews and hang them on their feet up on the wall, and with their head down, and would beat them up.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or hang them up-- had their hands with their feet down, and with whips.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so much shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember one of the first incidents, I-- we stand-- stood on the assembly square where we had to go two or three times a day to be counted.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
